description: Ready to find your zen? Listen to a koan and practice meditating upon this question or paradox. Just say "Alexa, ask ZenMaster for a koan" or more simply "Alexa, begin ZenMaster".
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask ZenMaster for a koan
Alexa, ask ZenMaster to give me a koan
Alexa, tell ZenMaster to begin zen practice
name: ZenMaster
shortDescription: ZenMaster tells you a koan that will help you practice meditation.
